Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:06.45,0:00:10.15,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let Me Be With You
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.60,0:00:22.00,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ふたりがきっと　出会えるような　魔法をかけて
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.60,0:00:22.00,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,施展了倆人一定會相遇的魔法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.75,0:00:29.10,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,両手をそっと　重ねてほら　ほほえむから
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.75,0:00:29.10,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悄悄的合起雙手 你看 在微笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:31.35,0:00:38.40,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ほんとの気持ち　気付かないふりして
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:31.35,0:00:38.40,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的心情 卻當作沒有察覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:38.50,0:00:48.15,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然ふたり　恋に落ちたの
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:38.50,0:00:48.15,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然 倆人陷入了愛河
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:50.20,0:00:53.90,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let Me Be With You
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:57.50,0:01:01.20,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let Me Be With You
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:04.70,0:01:08.40,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let Me Be With You
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:11.85,0:01:17.60,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,だきしめたいのに
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:11.85,0:01:17.60,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然很想擁抱你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:19.10,0:01:22.70,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let Me Be With You
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:26.50,0:01:30.20,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let Me Be With You
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:38.32,0:01:39.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夏天就快到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:40.96,0:01:43.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是我的第18個夏天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:45.00,0:01:45.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.00,0:01:47.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對身為重考生的我而言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.63,0:01:50.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在是不是夏天都沒關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.60,0:01:53.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最重要的是用功
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.20,0:01:56.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,次等重要的還是用功
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.62,0:02:06.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,成績一直都沒什麼進步耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.52,0:02:09.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對…對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.69,0:02:11.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別那麼沮喪嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.66,0:02:12.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.99,0:02:14.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你這個夏天努力用功的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.06,0:02:18.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秋天就一定能看到成果的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.40,0:02:21.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真…真的嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.17,0:02:22.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.17,0:02:23.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說得也對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.57,0:02:25.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為夏天是關鍵時刻嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.70,0:02:26.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會加油的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.31,0:02:29.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯，本須和，加油吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.34,0:02:31.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.81,0:03:07.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,學長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.11,0:03:10.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,裕…裕美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.62,0:03:12.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這件泳裝你覺得如何？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.42,0:03:14.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這可是為了今天而買的喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.62,0:03:16.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很…很合適啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.59,0:03:17.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,非常合適
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.39,0:03:19.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.82,0:03:21.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天是個大晴天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.19,0:03:25.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,清…清水老師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.57,0:03:30.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來，ちぃ衣服換好了喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.37,0:03:32.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,日比谷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.64,0:03:36.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.41,0:03:38.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.81,0:03:43.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.12,0:03:45.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.29,0:03:52.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,該怎麼說呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.22,0:03:54.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我真的到海邊來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.13,0:03:56.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我明明是個重考生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.60,0:04:00.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我真的能待在這裡嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.60,0:04:02.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,模擬考成績拿D的我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.03,0:04:05.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,貧窮又無暇的我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.81,0:04:10.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯，本須和，加油吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.31,0:04:11.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.38,0:04:14.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼，週末海邊見囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.71,0:04:16.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,海邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.95,0:04:19.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新保應該已經跟你說了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.09,0:04:23.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三天兩夜？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.32,0:04:24.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.16,0:04:25.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你一定也會去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.96,0:04:26.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,海邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.62,0:04:28.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.26,0:04:29.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我又沒那個錢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.06,0:04:31.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽我說嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.70,0:04:32.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,國分寺他說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.06,0:04:35.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,每年的這個時候\N都會到海邊的別墅去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.27,0:04:39.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而我們要跟他一起同行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.44,0:04:41.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以是免費的喔，免費的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.34,0:04:42.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,免費…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.84,0:04:45.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不…不過我們可是重考生耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.71,0:04:47.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼能去海邊啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.05,0:04:49.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本須和先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.41,0:04:50.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.48,0:04:53.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ泳裝穿這件好嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.22,0:04:55.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是我的舊衣服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.15,0:04:56.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.15,0:04:58.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管理員小姐我也邀請了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.42,0:05:00.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有，那女孩叫裕美吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.12,0:05:02.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家都說要去呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.29,0:05:03.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你真的不去嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.20,0:05:05.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀，本須和先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.83,0:05:07.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你很忙嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.50,0:05:10.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，沒這回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.40,0:05:14.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.94,0:05:17.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克服夏天考驗吧，重考生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.38,0:05:19.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我真的沒問題嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.15,0:05:26.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,#13         ちぃ，去海邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.02,0:05:30.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本須和
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.19,0:05:32.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她是電腦吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.29,0:05:33.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.09,0:05:36.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ，跟裕美\N還有清水老師打聲招呼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.63,0:05:37.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,晚安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.63,0:05:39.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.73,0:05:40.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在是中午吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.97,0:05:42.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用白天的打招呼法，ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.03,0:05:43.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.77,0:05:45.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,午安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.00,0:05:47.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,午安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.57,0:05:49.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯，ちぃ真是了不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.84,0:05:51.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好可愛的電腦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.74,0:05:53.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請多指教喔，ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.38,0:05:55.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.85,0:05:58.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂！本須和
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.72,0:06:00.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你還要杵在那裡多久啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.35,0:06:06.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,遊玩的時間會被耗光的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.69,0:06:07.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去幫幫本須和
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.67,0:06:16.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.84,0:06:22.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,1、2、3、4
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.04,0:06:25.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,2、2、3、4
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.84,0:06:28.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,3、2、3、4
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.88,0:06:31.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有好多水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.65,0:06:34.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，這裡就叫作“海”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.15,0:06:36.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,海？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.12,0:06:36.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.52,0:06:39.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,海
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.26,0:06:47.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.77,0:06:50.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家要不要一起去玩水？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.33,0:06:51.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.07,0:06:57.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡的海域\N深度不均勻，要小心喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.34,0:06:58.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.98,0:07:03.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,簡直像是小狗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.35,0:07:05.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼難得的機會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.98,0:07:07.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好好享受怎麼行呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.37,0:07:25.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呸，好…好鹹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.80,0:07:27.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誰叫你要東張西望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.94,0:07:31.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鹹？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.24,0:07:32.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯，沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.34,0:07:34.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,海水是鹹的，ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.68,0:07:37.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鹹水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.82,0:07:45.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了\N電腦碰到鹽水不會有事嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.82,0:07:46.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.49,0:07:51.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,電腦都有做日常防水\N所以沒關係的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.03,0:07:54.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊，說得也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.00,0:08:00.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,學長對電腦也很溫柔呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.24,0:08:04.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有機會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.68,0:08:06.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,竟敢潑我水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.38,0:08:14.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要不要一起游到那裡去？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.79,0:08:15.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好主意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.72,0:08:19.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不會游泳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.62,0:08:20.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我放棄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.46,0:08:24.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.46,0:08:26.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.43,0:08:29.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不勉強你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.03,0:08:31.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過，本須和
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.57,0:08:33.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,晚上我可不會讓你溜掉的喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.54,0:08:35.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,晚…晚上嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.67,0:08:37.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是說…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.64,0:08:42.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我幫你上特別課程
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.32,0:08:49.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,做好覺悟喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.19,0:08:52.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.69,0:08:59.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,竟然會有間別墅在這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.80,0:09:02.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你家果然真有錢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.57,0:09:03.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒那回事啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.20,0:09:06.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過這是那個對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.60,0:09:08.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所謂的私人海灘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.61,0:09:09.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.74,0:09:12.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是沒人來這裡玩罷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.28,0:09:15.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了，檢測結束
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.58,0:09:16.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.88,0:09:18.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.38,0:09:21.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們會不會打擾到你們了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.79,0:09:22.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.75,0:09:25.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為大家吵吵鬧鬧的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.02,0:09:27.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,確實是有點吵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.76,0:09:32.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今年的確比較熱鬧呢\N稔少爺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.13,0:09:32.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,的確
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.50,0:09:36.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過偶而這樣也不錯吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.10,0:09:37.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.24,0:09:39.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.71,0:09:42.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都到了這裡，不需要看書吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.04,0:09:45.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來玩吧！來玩吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.01,0:09:47.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.32,0:09:56.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好，去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.52,0:10:00.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要去囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.69,0:10:04.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要去囉，ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.56,0:10:06.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加油
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.77,0:10:13.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,球，秀樹給我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.81,0:10:17.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要開動了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.85,0:10:27.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.26,0:10:35.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好，開始吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.13,0:10:36.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好，開始吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.84,0:10:54.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所謂的幸福應該就是如此吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.85,0:10:57.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是個不錯的轉換心情方式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.35,0:11:01.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我可沒忘記要用功喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.19,0:11:04.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已經打算今夏要\N從早到晚苦讀了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.02,0:11:05.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是，是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.53,0:11:10.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我輸了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.10,0:11:14.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接著來玩撲克吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.74,0:11:23.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我記得清水老師的房間應該是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.44,0:11:25.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.35,0:11:34.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,晚上我會幫你上特別課程
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.99,0:11:37.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,晚上的課程是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.39,0:11:40.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一段夏季的回憶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.66,0:11:42.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,之類的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.23,0:11:46.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誰？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.83,0:11:48.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是本須和
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.40,0:11:51.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,門沒鎖，請進
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.64,0:11:52.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.34,0:12:00.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？進來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.45,0:12:07.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.09,0:12:12.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒人缺席吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.19,0:12:16.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.96,0:12:20.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就開始上課吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.23,0:12:23.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.51,0:12:34.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.38,0:12:36.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,起來了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.81,0:12:38.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也拿去抹吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.62,0:12:41.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是啥？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.75,0:12:45.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,電腦用的防腐蝕膏啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.32,0:12:49.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為海風、鹽水跟沙粒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.19,0:12:52.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都算是精密儀器的天敵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.20,0:12:53.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最好還是抹一下比較好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.93,0:12:56.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是，不是有日常防水了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.13,0:12:58.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,話雖如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.77,0:13:00.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是幫她保養一下比較好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.61,0:13:04.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,均勻的塗抹在全身就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.38,0:13:05.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很簡單吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.34,0:13:06.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這…這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.64,0:13:08.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,均勻的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.38,0:13:09.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.58,0:13:10.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要我抹嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.88,0:13:12.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要我幫ちぃ抹嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.75,0:13:15.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,3、2、1
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.89,0:13:16.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.89,0:13:18.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,辦…辦不到啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.56,0:13:21.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…我怎麼辦得到嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.06,0:13:24.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就教她自己塗抹吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.93,0:13:26.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.30,0:13:29.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.10,0:13:31.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.60,0:13:34.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.27,0:13:35.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.74,0:13:36.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽好喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.51,0:13:39.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先將防護膏像這樣擠出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.38,0:13:41.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是這樣啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.68,0:13:44.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.08,0:13:48.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本須和先生\N要不要我來幫忙？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.32,0:13:50.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麻煩妳了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.26,0:13:52.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,稍等一下喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.67,0:14:04.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,傳得好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.95,0:14:20.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹，這是什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.52,0:14:21.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.05,0:14:23.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，那是貝類，ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.02,0:14:29.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,貝類，那這個呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.76,0:14:32.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，那也是貝類
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.83,0:14:35.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,貝類，這也是貝類嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.13,0:14:36.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯，沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.00,0:14:39.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會走的貝類？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.10,0:14:41.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是，不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.44,0:14:44.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，這個叫什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.24,0:14:45.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是那個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.68,0:14:47.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,寄居蟹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.91,0:14:49.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是寄居蟹啦，本須和
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.88,0:14:51.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對喔對喔，叫寄居蟹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.92,0:14:53.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那叫寄居蟹喔，ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.55,0:14:54.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,寄居蟹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.25,0:14:56.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在教她詞句嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.95,0:14:58.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.49,0:15:00.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ現在還有很多事不懂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.99,0:15:02.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我如果不教她的話…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.79,0:15:03.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.56,0:15:05.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.80,0:15:09.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是昆布嗎？\N不，是裙帶菜嗎？還是海藻？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.77,0:15:11.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叫海草不就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.27,0:15:12.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.27,0:15:13.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,海草，那是海草，ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.10,0:15:15.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,海草
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.47,0:15:16.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是海草
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.34,0:15:19.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.58,0:15:20.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼，那是什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.95,0:15:21.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等啊，ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.41,0:15:23.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹，那是什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.98,0:15:27.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要不要我也來幫忙？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.42,0:15:29.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，拜…拜託妳了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.26,0:15:37.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好睏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.66,0:15:39.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我小睡一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.05,0:15:55.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.11,0:15:58.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.15,0:16:07.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是…是海豚耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.39,0:16:10.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,海…海豚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.59,0:16:11.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,海豚，是海豚啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.70,0:16:15.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ，妳的眼力真好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.70,0:16:16.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.77,0:16:18.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂，大家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.54,0:16:20.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有海豚耶，海豚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.27,0:16:22.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,牠們偶而會來啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.61,0:16:24.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊，這不是很棒嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.01,0:16:27.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只在電視上看過海豚耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.81,0:16:29.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也只在水族館看過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.48,0:16:31.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喔，這裡也有啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.25,0:16:35.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然有點遠\N不過真的有看到對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.22,0:16:37.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果能近一點看就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.69,0:16:39.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道會不會游到這附近來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.79,0:16:44.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說到近，如果游到這種近海來\N不就回不去了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.03,0:16:46.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對…對喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.56,0:16:48.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過很少有這種機會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.97,0:16:50.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還真想多看一點呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.24,0:16:54.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就游到外面一點去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.47,0:16:56.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應該沒多遠吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.11,0:17:01.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,學…學長，難道…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.41,0:17:05.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,昨天你說不會游泳\N不是開玩笑的啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.92,0:17:08.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我幹嘛拿這個來開玩笑啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.49,0:17:09.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不…不過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.59,0:17:12.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好歹也會蛙式吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.66,0:17:14.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.06,0:17:16.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.83,0:17:21.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,任誰都有擅長\N與不擅長的東西嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.30,0:17:23.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對啊，學長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.80,0:17:26.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這不是很好嗎，本須和
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.20,0:17:28.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聯考不考游泳這科目
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.31,0:17:30.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹不會游泳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.91,0:17:32.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那樣很厲害嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.38,0:17:33.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹很厲害嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.58,0:17:36.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,海豚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.85,0:17:38.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明明就在眼前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.92,0:17:42.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真拿你沒辦法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.86,0:17:50.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.26,0:17:53.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,私人遊艇耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.16,0:17:54.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對…對啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.63,0:17:58.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,突然覺得有點火
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.47,0:18:00.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這世界這樣真的好嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.04,0:18:02.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不會很不公平嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.37,0:18:05.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好棒啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.14,0:18:10.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果要觀賞海豚\N這一帶是最佳地點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.04,0:18:33.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好棒喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.34,0:18:35.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛那個妳有看到嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.01,0:18:39.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹看到海豚的“嘩啦”\N會很高興嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.38,0:18:40.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那當然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.84,0:18:42.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，妳看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.21,0:18:45.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.62,0:18:49.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.72,0:18:53.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘩啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.89,0:18:56.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,高興
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.33,0:19:05.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ也要來嘩啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.70,0:19:08.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.14,0:19:12.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.74,0:19:14.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.48,0:19:15.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ她…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.28,0:19:17.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡？在哪裡？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.75,0:19:19.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本須和，還不快去救她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.22,0:19:22.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過，反正她有日常防水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.25,0:19:23.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.15,0:19:26.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼深的地方\N日常防水一點用也沒有啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.59,0:19:27.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.00,0:19:32.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本須和
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.20,0:19:33.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,學長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.93,0:19:35.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不是不會游泳嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.52,0:20:28.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.79,0:20:30.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,國分寺的別墅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.72,0:20:32.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的，學長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.16,0:20:33.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請不要這麼亂來啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.22,0:20:37.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對啊，不經思索就跳下去救人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.69,0:20:39.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真像你的作風
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.43,0:20:40.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對…對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.03,0:20:43.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小…ちぃ呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.87,0:20:48.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.41,0:20:51.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來妳沒事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.41,0:20:55.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ沒事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.08,0:20:57.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從表面看來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.38,0:20:59.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像也沒進水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.65,0:21:01.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹，你在生氣嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.92,0:21:04.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ做錯事了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.32,0:21:05.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會生氣呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:05.62,0:21:07.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳沒事就好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.39,0:21:08.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.63,0:21:10.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.00,0:21:14.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖說如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.40,0:21:16.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她真是台不可思議的電腦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.40,0:21:18.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一般如果掉到海裡的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.77,0:21:20.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就會進水，然後會很難修復
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.24,0:21:22.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:22.74,0:21:25.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過如果ちぃ發生事情的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.54,0:21:28.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或許會變得更麻煩呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:28.35,0:21:29.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是真的喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.08,0:21:35.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,救本須和起來的可是ちぃ喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:36.79,0:21:38.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:38.36,0:21:40.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝妳，ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:48.40,0:21:50.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,1、2、3、4
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:50.73,0:21:51.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,2、2…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:53.04,0:21:54.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的夏天結束了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:57.37,0:21:58.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最重要的是用功
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:58.31,0:21:59.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,次等重要的還是用功
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:59.74,0:22:01.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個夏天是關鍵時刻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:01.31,0:22:02.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,目標是成績進步
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:05.45,0:22:07.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,成績竟然又退步了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:25.74,0:22:31.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不經意的走在熟悉的街道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:31.64,0:22:38.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,的確會照映在眼簾中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:40.55,0:22:46.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在成群結隊前進的人群中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:46.66,0:22:53.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那顆遭到淹沒         感到膽怯的心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:55.53,0:22:59.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Raison         d'etre         像那種感覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:59.30,0:23:02.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Raison         d'etre         如同那般的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:02.41,0:23:10.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,歡笑、沉沒、漂流\N究竟是為了什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:10.51,0:23:14.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,尋找著那把鑰匙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:14.25,0:23:17.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不斷的在尋找著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:17.42,0:23:21.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼都找不到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:21.73,0:23:27.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那扇門的鑰匙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:41.81,0:23:43.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹，夏天熱嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:43.88,0:23:46.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯，夏天真熱啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:46.42,0:23:49.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,整個人昏沉沉的，一點精神都沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:50.05,0:23:51.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夏天要用蚊香嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:51.69,0:23:53.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:53.12,0:23:56.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蚊香的味道\N可說是夏天的必需品啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:57.23,0:23:59.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夏天清水老師會來嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:59.30,0:24:00.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯，沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:00.20,0:24:02.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夏天還是清水老師最棒啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:05.07,0:24:07.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chobits         下一回\N「ちぃ，招待」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:07.94,0:24:08.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,樂意之至
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:09.04,0:24:10.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,樂意之至
